{
  "texts": [
    "It is accompanied by an online course in the university's learning management system Moodle.The class consists of a 2-hour lecture per week for all students, and a 2-hour tutorial session in groups of 20-30 students.",
    "In the tutorial, students are supposed to solve weekly or bi-weekly exercise sheets with programming problems.",
    "Even though this is voluntary, students can collect points for correct submissions (two for the exercises required for this study).",
    "These points can later be used to improve exam grades.For this study, a new exercise sheet was developed for one of the tutorial sessions.",
    "Students were asked to individually work on these exercises for two weeks from December 6 onwards."
  ]
}